// GE Profile brand pillar (~2k words). Built 2026-05-11. Tone reference:
// brands/ge-monogram.astro pattern (same GE family, refrigerator-led
// positioning). Primary keyword: "GE Profile refrigerator repair Los
// Angeles" (800 vol, KD 0, $300 CPC). Voice discipline: refrigerator-
// led across hero + intro + section 02 + recent repairs, TwinChill
// evaporator dual-zone failure pattern (2017-2022 PFE28 French Door
// cohort with the signature "fridge warm, freezer fine" symptom),
// SmartDispense automated detergent dosing distinction (software vs
// hardware diagnostic split), WiFi Connect / SmartHQ app remote
// monitoring as cosmetic-not-functional service item (firmware vs
// hardware), Profile-vs-Monogram-vs-Café tier hierarchy (different
// chassis, different control boards), Haier-ownership clarification
// (acquired 2016, US parts network intact, Louisville KY HQ),
